			"description":"Traintrack family, traintrack_L7_massless-internal-offshell-external. Planar chain of L boxes (cells), massless internal lines. External legs at every vertex: 4 off-shell corners (distinct masses, the collapsed pairs of the paper's 2L+6 massless particles) + 2L-2 massless middle legs; L=1 is the four-mass box. The L-loop traintrack is a weight-(L+1) hyperlogarithm over a Calabi-Yau (L-1)-fold: L=1 is a box, L=2 elliptic, L=3 a K3 surface, L=4 a Calabi-Yau threefold.",
